\fs24 \cf0 Ch\uc0\u432 \u417 ng 1: Ph\u7847 n chung
\f0\b0  (10\uc0\u273 )\
M\uc0\u7909 c 1.1 gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u JulieCosmetics: th\'e0nh l\u7853 p khi n\'e0o, b\'e1n g\'ec, m\'f4 h\'ecnh B2C, t\u7847 m nh\'ecn. L\u7845 y 70% t\u7915  ph\u7847 n gi\u7899 i thi\u7879 u HAL luxury r\u7891 i rewrite context m\u7929  ph\u7849 m \'97 t\u7889 n kho\u7843 ng 1 bu\u7893 i. M\u7909 c 1.2 b\u7843 ng kh\u7843 o s\'e1t 15 c\'e2u: ph\u7843 i vi\u7871 t m\u7899 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n, t\'f4i c\'f3 th\u7875  vi\u7871 t s\u7861 n cho b\u7841 n ngay khi b\u7841 n y\'eau c\u7847 u. M\u7909 c 1.3 t\u7893 ng k\u7871 t kh\u7843 o s\'e1t.\

\f1\b Ch\uc0\u432 \u417 ng 2: Ph\'e2n t\'edch HTTT
\f0\b0  (10\uc0\u273 )\
M\uc0\u7909 c 2.1 m\'f4 t\u7843  ho\u7841 t \u273 \u7897 ng doanh nghi\u7879 p (t\'e1i d\u7909 ng c\u7845 u tr\'fac HAL luxury, th\'eam nh\'e1nh nh\'e2n s\u7921  v\'e0 kho). M\u7909 c 2.2 s\u417  \u273 \u7891  ch\u7913 c n\u259 ng BFD. M\u7909 c 2.3 s\u417  \u273 \u7891  ng\u7919  c\u7843 nh. M\u7909 c 2.4 DFD m\u7913 c \u273 \u7881 nh (m\u7913 c 1). M\u7909 c 2.5 DFD m\u7913 c d\u432 \u7899 i \u273 \u7881 nh (m\u7913 c 2, chi ti\u7871 t t\u7915 ng ch\u7913 c n\u259 ng l\u7899 n \'97 \u273 \'e2y l\'e0 ph\u7847 n hay b\u7883  thi\u7871 u nh\u7845 t). C\u7845 u tr\'fac s\u417  \u273 \u7891  t\'e1i d\u7909 ng t\u7915  HAL luxury, b\u7893  sung th\'eam nh\'e1nh nh\'e2n s\u7921 .\

\f1\b Ch\uc0\u432 \u417 ng 3: Thi\u7871 t k\u7871  HTTT
\f0\b0  (10\uc0\u273 )\
M\uc0\u7909 c 3.1 thi\u7871 t k\u7871  CSDL: l\u432 \u7907 c \u273 \u7891  quan h\u7879  + b\u7843 ng m\'f4 t\u7843  t\u7915 ng b\u7843 ng (b\u7843 ng nh\'e2n vi\'ean, b\u7843 ng ch\u7913 c v\u7909 , b\u7843 ng \u273 \u417 n ngh\u7881  ph\'e9p, b\u7843 ng l\u432 \u417 ng l\'e0 m\u7899 i ho\'e0n to\'e0n; b\u7843 ng s\u7843 n ph\u7849 m/\u273 \u417 n h\'e0ng/KH t\'e1i d\u7909 ng t\u7915  HAL luxury v\'e0 \u273 i\u7873 u ch\u7881 nh). M\u7909 c 3.2 thi\u7871 t k\u7871  giao di\u7879 n: screenshot m\u7895 i m\'e0n h\'ecnh quan tr\u7885 ng + m\'f4 t\u7843 .\

\f1\b Ch\uc0\u432 \u417 ng 4: C\'e0i \u273 \u7863 t v\'e0 b\u7843 o tr\'ec
\f0\b0  (5\uc0\u273 )\
